FBIS4-58271 "drnes085_o_94002" FBIS-NES-94-085 Daily Report 2 May 1994 SYRIA Citizens Support Policy To Restore Golan Citizens Support Policy To Restore Golan JN0205135894 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in Arabic 1115 GMT 2 May 94 JN0205135894 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network Arabic BFN [Text] Occupied Golan -- Syrian Arab citizens have declared their support for Syria's efforts to restore occupied Syrian Golan and to realize a full Israeli withdrawal from it. In a statement issued yesterday and distributed in several cities and villages, the Syrian Arab citizens in the occupied Golan also expressed support for Syria's policy and principled stands toward the restoration of all of the Golan to Syria.
